FBIS3-41286 "jptdd007__l94076" JPRS-TDD-94-007-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Narcotics 14 February 1994 WEST EUROPE TURKEY 2.5 Tonnes of Hashish Seized in Van Province TA0502091594 Ankara ANATOLIA in English 1000 GMT 3 Feb 94 TA0502091594 Ankara ANATOLIA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Van, Feb 3 (AA) -- 2.5 tonnes of hashish, hidden in 91 sacks were seized in Baskale township in eastern Van Province on Wednesday. AA was told that security forces acting on a tip off staged an operation in Sinova region in Ekecek village in Baskale township. The market value of the hashish was 50 billion Turkish lira [approximately $2,500,000]. An investigation has been launched into the incident.
